Mialitiana Clerc (amụrụ na 16 Nọvemba afọ 2001 na Ambohitrimanjaka, Madagascar) bụ onye na-agba ọsọ n'elu ugwu si Madagascar. Clerc sonyere Madagascar na afọ 2018 Winter Olympics na ihe omume skiing alpine
Clerc ghọrọ nwanyị mbụ na-asọmpi maka Madagascar na Winter Olympics. A mụrụ Clerc na Madagascar, otu ezinụlọ French kuchiri ya mgbe ọ dị otu afọ
Ọ mụtara ịgba ọsọ na France.
